no params, stub). This does NOT match the PRD/exec plan which specifies:\n   - `
POST /auth/login` (phone + sms_code, register+login合一)\n   - `POST /auth/refre
sh`\n   - `POST /auth/logout`\n   - `GET /auth/me`\n\n2. **Auth Service**: Mostl
y stubbed. `register` just checks age and returns stub user_id. `login` returns 
