eature files exist but step definitions are all empty (`() => {}`). The auth ser
vice spec only tests age validation.\n\n6. **Docs**: `docs/modules/auth.md` refe
rences files that don't exist (jwt-auth.guard.ts, Flutter BLoC).\n\n7. **Shared 
types**: Has generated auth types, but they seem to be from an OpenAPI contract 
that may not match the current implementation.\n\n8. **DB entities**: `users` an
d `user_profiles` tables exist with proper schema.\n\nWait - I should check if t
