g all the key areas.\n\nKey findings so far:\n1. **Auth Controller**: Has `POST 
/api/v1/auth/register` (takes phone, birth_date) and `POST /api/v1/auth/login` (
no params, stub). This does NOT match the PRD/exec plan which specifies:\n   - `
POST /auth/login` (phone + sms_code, register+login合一)\n   - `POST /auth/refre
sh`\n   - `POST /auth/logout`\n   - `GET /auth/me`\n\n2. **Auth Service**: Mostl
y stubbed. `register` just checks age and returns stub user_id. `login` returns 
stub tokens. No SMS validation, no real user creation, no JWT generation, no Red
is integration.\n\n3. **Mobile**: Only has `main.dart` with a placeholder scaffo
ld. No BLoC, no login page, no secure storage, no interceptor.\n\n4. **Guards**:
